{"tid":1915481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】恐殺入重慶大廈 首度有家居檢疫者懷疑染疫","createTime":"2020-03-08T08:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T11:05:58.000Z","uid":227650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c9418140967331e82af522aaee908de28b57bc","tid":1915481,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200308&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60688148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200308%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60688148&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=fcddb0e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200308%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60688148&h=aa9afb08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200308&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60688148</a>"},{"pid":"63281748dd46f13a0cc21fbf0b5921137e9c19ea","tid":1915481,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40b22bba120009bcc09596f1352bcf609ace73b","tid":1915481,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"最後避難所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebd67003ab8e977371f7a146b87fccbc0c29bd2","tid":1915481,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"高乜撚嘢度懷疑"},{"pid":"c440ab15c4789dc523c5e342cb17a498a7094825","tid":1915481,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"有肺炎即係重慶大廈奶共了唉"},{"pid":"5400e770aaa0b669a03fda6bb8634558ce4b9eba","tid":1915481,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"本港微生物學權威專家袁國勇今早在電視節目時警告，本港必須留意本港南亞人士聚居的社區，會否出現確診個案。言猶在耳，《蘋果》接獲消息，伊利沙伯醫院今天接收一名居於尖沙嘴重慶大廈、正接受家居檢疫的男子求醫，其樣本經第一輪武漢肺炎快速測試後，暫時列為高度懷疑個案；若他最終確診，將是全港首位家居隔離期間染疫患者。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該名55歲男子居於重慶大廈，報稱2月中下旬曾到過深圳及廣西，3月1日回港接受14天家居檢疫，今（8日）到伊院求醫。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，男病人無發燒，肺片暫未發現肺炎迹象，但有喉嚨痛，故院方安排他接受隔離，同時抽取樣本做快速測試。據悉，第一輪快速測試後，暫時把他列為高度懷疑個案，需要覆檢作實，料今天稍後時間有第二輪結果。"},{"pid":"d5470a0fb672f7f73d33324893e85cf4a565d554","tid":1915481,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cebd67003ab8e977371f7a146b87fccbc0c29bd2","tid":1915481,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"高乜撚嘢度懷疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"語言偽術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef03c94d4187a41261ea12630abd4974977e86eb","tid":1915481,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53eafcc90b2849ce26398b6ef8bde0c9c33bb0af","tid":1915481,"uid":159852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"屌 仲返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8341ce449b4c0cc82611e9830532fab903ef4f","tid":1915481,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈啲賓館密到咁，大爆發了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486ab3f8d605cab93b6ad808b9eceb7033dc25e1","tid":1915481,"uid":103619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af8341ce449b4c0cc82611e9830532fab903ef4f","tid":1915481,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈啲賓館密到咁，大爆發了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:05:58.000Z","